  <brief_title>Joint Status in Subjects With Severe Hemophilia A in Relation to Different Treatment Regimens</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Diagnostic Interventional, Controlled, Cross-sectional Evaluation of Joint Status Using Magnetic Resonance Imaging in Subjects With Severe Hemophilia A Treated With Primary Prophylaxis, Secondary Prophylaxis, or On-demand Therapy</official_title>
