  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The joint status (knees, ankles) of patients suffering from severe Hemophilia A (too little
      blood clotting factor VIII in blood) is evaluated in a single magnetic resonance imaging
      session. No study medication is given.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
